WEBVTT

00:10:02.065 --> 00:10:03.479
He also told me

00:10:03.503 --> 00:10:06.649
that if the State of Mississippi
wanted to keep the death penalty,

00:10:06.673 --> 00:10:11.780
then hey, they needed to provide
counseling for the jurors.

00:10:12.941 --> 00:10:15.910
Then the next juror I met was Jane.

00:10:15.934 --> 00:10:18.666
Jane is now totally
against the death penalty,

00:10:19.273 --> 00:10:20.639
And there was Bill.

00:10:21.394 --> 00:10:26.653
Bill said he had this
crushing depression for weeks,

00:10:26.677 --> 00:10:28.760
and when he went back to work,

00:10:28.784 --> 00:10:32.091
his colleagues would say
